Text.val: get number of recently uploaded files to display (maximum)
returns a list of all recently uploaded file
This is required for Poland where manual invoice entry actually
is a file upload and where the users want to see qnd download all recently

SQL_STMT_U.val: select IFIL_ID, IFIL_SESSIONID,IFIL_DATE, IFIL_TIME from :1/ifil a inner join :2/icrh b on a.IFIL_SESSIONID=ICRH_ICSE_ID where ICRH_ICSE_CUSR_ADMNO=:3 and ICRH_ICSE_CUSR_CLNTNO=:4 group by IFIL_ID, IFIL_SESSIONID, IFIL_DATE, IFIL_TIME order by IFIL_DATE DESC,IFIL_TIME DESC

to the number stored in GSET(6021) by setting end task condition
